name: macaque_BG_genepanels
title: Gene panel comparison for Macaque Basal Ganglia
description:
Correlation scrattch-mapping of one section with different gene sets produced from various gene panel making methods. Gene expression values of -1 indicates that that gene was not present in the subpanel

VZG601 = full panel (455 genes)

geneBasis: subcortial = geneBasis method using subcortical taxonomy (176 genes)

He + markers = genes from He et al paper + internal BG marker genes (105 genes)

geneBasis: whole brain = geneBasisi method using cortical and subcortical taxonomy (140 genes)

geneBasis + He + markers = geneBasis subcortical and He + markers (295 genes)
